resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Le kojkemchak Wachib'al kuk'ut taq le wachib'al chi'l le k'olsilob'wach pa taq le awiqkmechakub'al xa pa jun k'olib'al. .

Are chi kawil taq wachib'al chi'l k'olsilob'wach pa jun chik kematz'ib', chatok pa la' le kematz'ib', chasolij SkyDrive.com/windows chi'l chaqasaj on chakojo' Microsoft SkyDrive. K'ate k'u ri', chatika' kemchak pa le akemb'i'aj Microsoft qas chawila' chi le alaj k'olib'al Uk'amik taq le kemk'olonik apawije' k'olib'al e t'iqitalik.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: We k'o jujun awech, qas chawila' chi keriqitaj pa le k'olno'j kemchak rech taq wachib'al {{%1}}.

resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive kutzukuj apan le uk'olik taq le wachib'al, le silab'wachib'al, le tz'ib'wuj che na tojtal taj, are chi utz katok chi rilik apawij' at k'o wi.

Chasolij SkyDrive.com are chi katokik. Le wachib'al chi'l taq le silob'wachib'al ak'olom chila' ke'ilitaj waral.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Are chi kamajij, chat'iqa' jun wiqkemchakub'al (esab'al wachib'a, ch'aweb'al, ujunalil flash USB, nik'aj chik) chataqa' on chawachib'ej taq wachib'al chi'l k'olsilob'wach pa le k'olno'j kemchak rech taq wachib'al.

We k'o chi awachib'al chi'l k'olsilob'wach pa we kematz'ib', chak'amb'ejaj chi e k'o pa le k'ono'j kemchak rech wachib'al. Chab'ana' kemchajinik chi rech le k'olno'j kemchak rech taq wachib'al pa jun Utzukk'utunel rech kemk'olonik.
